rows.label: qst202104_0010
rows.name: Heeey[ML:Dash ] This is amazing.

rows.label: qst202104_0020
rows.name: Oh, what on earth is this?

rows.label: qst202104_0030
rows.name: She's already completely absorbed in it[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202104_0040
rows.name: That's just like Shiki.

rows.label: qst202104_0050
rows.name:
Good grief[ML:Dash ] Acting alone
is dangerous, Shiki[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202104_0060
rows.name: Wait, Nia.

rows.label: qst202104_0070
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Hm?

rows.label: qst202104_0080
rows.name: There is something inside the room[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202104_0090
rows.name: Enemy!

rows.label: qst202104_0100
rows.name: The guardian of this room, it seems[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202104_0110
rows.name: Shiki! It's dangerous there!

rows.label: qst202104_0120
rows.name: No good. She ain't listenin'.

rows.label: qst202104_0130
rows.name: Bad, mo! It's targeting Shiki, mo!

rows.label: qst202104_0140
rows.name: Shiki! Run!

rows.label: qst202104_0150
rows.name:
What is it? You're noisy. I can't
concentrate on the investigation[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202104_0160
rows.name: Ah[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202104_0170
rows.name:
You came to obstruct my
investigation, didn't you[ML:Dash ] Just
when it was at the best part[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202104_0180
rows.name:
I don't want anyone disturbing
my intellectual curiosity
and spirit of inquiry.

rows.label: qst202104_0190
rows.name:
If you understand, read
the room and stay quiet!

rows.label: qst202104_0200
rows.name:
Oi oi, Shiki's gonna start
all by herself, ya know?

rows.label: qst202104_0210
rows.name: Let's go too, Rex.
